dct_title_s: Midland County - Midland, Michigan, official road map 1971
dct_description_sm: Abstract: County road map and city street map.
Includes text, indexes to roads and streets, 3 ancillary maps, and illustrations.
Ancillary maps: City of Coleman, Midland County, Michigan -- Village of Sanford, Midland County, Michigan -- Midland area.
